527
00:53:50,777 --> 00:53:56,506
♫ that visited me one day ♫

528
00:53:56,507 --> 00:54:04,016
♫ Inside this cold story ♫

529
00:54:04,017 --> 00:54:11,526
♫ You are a warm place ♫

530
00:54:11,527 --> 00:54:19,527
